(45, 1, '2015-12-22 04:40:21', '2015-12-22 04:40:21', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"><var style="color: #1f497d; font-style: normal;">UNI</var>MEDIA</span>  QUNG CO TP CH V ONLINE</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>1. S lc v cng ty</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> mang sn phm, thng hiu n gn hn ngi tiu dng, cc doanh nghip  v ang thc hin rt nhiu hnh thc PR  Marketing vi mc chi ph khng nh, nhng  tr nn bo ha trong thi i hin nay.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">UNIMEDIA t ho cho ra mt n phm mang phong cch hon ton khc bit vi 100% qung co  pht trin thnh cng hn 15 nm ti th trng M. Chng ti tin chc UNIMEDIA s l la chn hng u cho cc doanh nghip  a sn phm, dch v ca mnh n tay ngi tiu dng mt cch nhanh chng v hiu qu nht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vi i ng nhn vin chuyn nghip, chng ti t tin em n cho khch hng cc dch v uy tn v cht lng. Lun lng nghe v bin nhu cu ca khch hng thnh ng lc  lm vic mi ngy,  l nim vui ca chng ti. Qung co tp ch v online UNIMEDIA pht hnh 6 n phm thuc nhng chuyn  ring bit vi s lng hn 100.000 bn mi k. Cc n phm qung co bao gm:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li><em><strong>Ngun a c (Real Estate Source):</strong></em> mang n cho bn c nhng thng tin nng hi v th trng bt ng sn, ni bn c th so snh v la chn cc sn phm bt ng sn uy tn v cht lng mt cch nhanh nht.</li>\r\n	<li><em><strong>m thc &amp; Tic (Taste &amp; Event):</strong></em> Cp nht nhng a im m thc phong ph cho bn v ngi thn.</li>\r\n	<li><em><strong>Thi trang &amp; Sc khe (Fashion &amp; Health):</strong> </em>p ngoi  Khe trong. Ni bn c th tm kim cc a ch tin cy  bn thn p ton din.</li>\r\n	<li><em><strong>in my &amp; Gia dng (Home &amp; Electronics):</strong></em> Nng tm cuc sng ca bn v gia nh. n phm cung cp y  cc sn phm t nhiu thng hiu khc nhau, trang b tin nghi, sung tc cho mi m ca bn.</li>\r\n	<li><em><strong>Xe &amp; Cng ngh (Vehicle &amp; Technology):</strong></em> Phong cch sng hin i v nhng sn phm cng ngh hng u s nm ngay trong tm tay bn khi s hu n phm ny.</li>\r\n	<li><strong><em>4 Ma &amp; Khuyn mi (4 Seasons &amp; Promotion):</em></strong> Cp nht nhanh chng cc chng trnh u i hp dn ca nhng ngnh hng khc nhau.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cc n phm dnh cho nhng con ngi hin i, nng ng v thnh t trong cuc sng; Cc doanh nhn ti ba, bn lnh, quyt on dn u thnh cng; Gii vn phng tr trungbit chn la phong cch sng  nng tm gi tr bn thn; Dn tr thc thng minh, c tnh, yu ci p v thchkhm ph cuc sng Khng dng li  , UNIMEDIA s m rng v pht trin lin tc  xy dng thng hiu cho khch hng, p ng mi nhu cu ca nhng khch hng kh tnh nht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>2. Tm nhn v s mnh</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bng kht vng tin phong cng chin lc hp tc  u t  pht trin bn vng, UNIMEDIA khng ngng n lc  tr thnh cng ty qung co tp ch &amp; online hng u ti Vit Nam. Chng ti, Qung co Tp ch &amp; Online UNIMEDIA, s l cu ni uy tn  mang khch hng n vi bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li><em>i vi c gi:</em> Mi n phm pht hnh u s hu phong cch hin i v sng to, m bo mc  tin cy, tha mn ti a nhu cu ca bn c.</li>\r\n	<li><em>i vi i tc:</em>  cao tinh thn hp tc cng pht trin v cam kt tr thnh ngi ng hnh s 1 ca i tc.</li>\r\n	<li><em>i vi nhn vin:</em> Xy dng mi trng lm vic nng ng, chuyn nghip v lun to iu kin pht trin cng bng cho tt c nhn vin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>3. Tim nng v th mnh</strong></p>\r\n<a href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/about-vi.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-401" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/about-vi.jpg" alt="about-vi" width="761" height="291" /></a>', 'Gii thiu', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gioi-thieu', '', '', '2016-01-07 07:45:16', '2016-01-07 07:45:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?page_id=45', 0, 'page', '', 0),
