(275, 1, '2016-01-07 02:49:07', '2016-01-07 02:49:07', '<div class="short_intro txt_666">Hng th th ni gi chnh lch, hng tng cng gim gi  thu ht khch hng dp mua sm cao im ma Tt.</div>\r\n<div id="left_calculator">\r\n<div class="fck_detail width_common">\r\n<p class="Normal">Cn gn mt thng na l Tt Nguyn n, theo thng l cc ca hng xe my bt u chun b cho ma mua sm si ng nht trong nm.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Ti cc Head ca Honda, lng khch bt u tng dn l lc mt lot xe tay ga ang c a chung rc rch tng gi. in hnh l dng SH  xc lp k lc tng gi mi l 93 triu ng cho bn 150 mu mi so vi gi hng cng b l 81 triu ng (chnh 12 triu ng).</p>\r\n\r\n<table class="tplCaption" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://img.f29.vnecdn.net/2016/01/06/2-9339-1452050282.jpg" alt="thi-truong-xe-may-trai-nguoc-mua-cuoi-nam" data-natural-width="500" data-width="500" data-pwidth="470.40625" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal">Va ra mt phin bn mi, Air Blade cng c gi chnh khong 3 triu ng cho mi phin bn. c bit, do phin bn Air Blade c vn c a chung m khng cn sn xut nn mc chnh cao hn ti 9 triu ng cho phin bn en m gi khong 49 triu ng v khch hng cng khng cn nhiu la chn mu cho phin bn ny.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Cc mu xe cn li nh Vision gi 33 -34 triu, Lead khong 40 - 42 triu. Cc loi xe s nh Dream, Wave... th hu nh khng p dng chnh gi hoc c chnh cng khng ng k.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Ngc li vi Honda, Yamaha li gim gi trong ma cao im. Nozza gim 900.000 ng, cn 28 triu so vi gi cng b l 28,9 triu ng. Grande c mc gim cao hn l 1,7 triu, cn 40,3 triu ng. Cc dng xe cn li cng c p dng mc gi gim t 1-2 triu.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Hng ny cn c chng trnh ng k i th nhm tng tri nghim. Ch Thu Hng, mt khch hng, chia s: "Ti thch dng chic Acruzo mi ra mt nhng cha bao gi s dng xe ga ca Yamaha nn cng c cht bn khon. Sau khi i th xe nu thch vn c th mua v ng k xe kp trc Tt".</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Mt nghch cnh gia Honda v Yamaha l phn khc xe th thao. Nu cc i l Honda ng lot gim gi mnh cho chic MSX, cn 58 triu so vi gi cng b l 60 triu. Th showroom Yamaha li p dng gi chnh kh cao cho Exciter phin bn Camo. Ti H Ni, Exciter c gi 51,5 triu cn khu vc TP HCM c gi ln ti 54 triu ( ra bin s) so vi gi cng b l 45,5 triu.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Ging nh Yamaha, thi gian ny Piaggio cng p dng gim gi khong 1 triu cho mi mu xe. Ring Primavera hng h tr khch hng 100% thu trc b.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Th trng xe my tri ngc ma cui nm', 'Hng th th ni gi chnh lch, hng tng cng gim gi  thu ht khch hng dp mua sm cao im ma Tt.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thi-truong-xe-may-trai-nguoc-mua-cuoi-nam', '', '', '2016-01-07 02:49:07', '2016-01-07 02:49:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=275', 0, 'post', '', 0),
