(279, 1, '2016-01-07 02:56:05', '2016-01-07 02:56:05', '<div class="short_intro txt_666">Cc mu Continental v Flying Spur hon thin vi gi Mulliner Bespoke s c thm ty chn p  c ngun gc t n .</div>\r\n<div id="left_calculator">\r\n<div class="fck_detail width_common">\r\n\r\nc ct t cc tm  ln, cc ming p c chiu dy ch 0,1 mm, s dng nh vt liu thay th nhng th truyn thng nh g v kim loi.  ct mng n mc siu nh v c phn trong sut, cho php cc th v hoa vn t nhin hin th r.  lm cng bng cch s dng si thy tinh v nha thng c bit trc khi to hnh v hon thin th cng vi mt trong s 4 mu ty chn.\r\n<table class="tplCaption" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://img.f29.vnecdn.net/2016/01/06/bentley-1-7435-1452070664.jpg" alt="bentley-dung-da-co-op-noi-that-xe" data-natural-width="500" data-width="500" data-pwidth="470.40625" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal">Ly ngun t cc bang Rajasthan v Pradesh  n , loi  p c cho l c tui i hng trm triu nm. y cng l ln u tin Bentley a ra ty chn ny trn dng sn phm siu sang. " p ch l s khi u ca nhng g chng ti ln k hoch vi cc loi vt liu sang trng v c o", Geoff Dowding, gim c chng trnh Mulliner cho bit.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Khch hng ca Bentley c th chn p  trn ton b b mt bng tp-l hoc ch mt phn. Chi ph ty thuc vo lng vt liu c s dng cho tng n hng.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Vi Bentley l ln u, nhng  p s dng trong ni tht xe  c hng khc ng dng trc . Citroen mi ra mt mu Crossback concept trong nm 2015 vi ni tht p  granite ly ngun t chnh nc Php v loi vt liu ny c d bo s xut hin nhiu hn trn cc mu xe trong tng lai gn.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Bentley dng  c p ni tht xe', 'Cc mu Continental v Flying Spur hon thin vi gi Mulliner Bespoke s c thm ty chn p  c ngun gc t n .', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bentley-dung-da-co-op-noi-that-xe', '', '', '2016-01-07 02:56:05', '2016-01-07 02:56:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=279', 0, 'post', '', 0),
