(281, 1, '2016-01-07 02:58:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>Hng xe Anh quc cho bit, nn tng khung nhm mi ang c hng th nghim trn mt mu<strong>Phantom</strong>, v s c cc kt lun nh gi khi n chy th trn hu khp cc mt ng cng cng.</p><p>Trong giai on th nghim u tin, <a class="TextlinkBaiviet" title="Rolls-Royce" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/rolls-royce-c77e2594.html">Rolls-Royce</a> ch yu tp trung vo vic m bo cu trc ca mu xe sao cho xng vi thng hiu m ngi ta thng v von xe chy m nh mt tm thm ma thut ca cng ty, trong khi vn m m bo c  bn cn thit v p ng c nhng iu kin thi tit v cng khc nghit.</p><p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-0" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-0" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452075707-1452066947-1.jpg" alt="L Rolls-Royce Phantom dng nn tng khung nhm mi - 1" /></span></p><p align="center">Nn tng khung nhm mi c Rolls-Royce th nghim trn mu Phantom v ngy trang kn mt</p><p>Pha cng ty t chi tit l nhng chi tit c th, nhng cu trc v nn tng ban u ca xe  tng xut hin vo u nm 2015. y l nn tng mi u tin m theo Rolls-Royce s c rt nhiu iu c bit, s sang trng bc nht, v c mc ch.</p><p>Khi tung ra th trng, chic off-road ny s c t tn l Cullinan, l tn mt vin kim cng th ln nht th gii c tm thy cho n nay. Chic SUV c ch to bng nhm  gi trng lng nh cho xe v pht trin trn h khung gm c cu trc hon ton mi cha c s dng cho bt k mu no.</p><p>Gim c iu hnh ca <em>Rolls-Royce</em>, ng Torsen Muller-Otvos chia s :"By gi l thi im  thc hin bc tip theo trong k hoch pht trin nhng mu xe sang trng nht ca hng. y l l do ti sao ti cng b vic th nghim mt kt cu c quyn hon ton mi ca Rolls-Royce  chnh thc c bt u. Kin trc mi ny l minh chng cho s u t ca Rolls-Royce cho vic pht trin nhng mu xe tng lai ca hng.</p><p>Trc , Bentley  gia nhp th trng SUV vi chic Bentayga v khng nh y l model sang trng nht trong phn khc ny, nhng CEO Rolls-Royce Torsten Muller Otvos p tr li rng Bentley SUV r rng ng  v tr th 2 v Rolls-Royce s chim v tr qun qun khi tung ra bn  i l vo cui nm 2018. Khi c hi liu Rolls-Royce s gi tn gi Cullinan hay khng, ng Muller ni rng ng thch ci tn ny, c ngha l chic SUV nhiu kh nng s ly tn theo vin kim cng th ln nht th gii.</p><p>Nhng thng s k thut ca chic xe vn bt v m tn, nhng mt s bo co trc  ni rng chic SUV siu sang ny s trang b ng c V12 6.75 lt. Ngoi ra, m hnh ny cng c n on s vay mn mt s thnh phn t ngi anh em BMW X7.</p>', 'L Rolls-Royce Phantom dng nn tng khung nhm mi', 'Mt mu Phantom ang c Rolls-Royce th nghim da trn nn tng khung nhm mi, v s p dng cho tt c cc mu xe ca hng t 2018.', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:00:47', '2016-01-07 03:00:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=281', 0, 'post', '', 0),
