(286, 1, '2016-01-07 03:00:47', '2016-01-07 03:00:47', '<p>Hng xe Anh quc cho bit, nn tng khung nhm mi ang c hng th nghim trn mt mu<strong>Phantom</strong>, v s c cc kt lun nh gi khi n chy th trn hu khp cc mt ng cng cng.</p><p>Trong giai on th nghim u tin, <a class="TextlinkBaiviet" title="Rolls-Royce" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/rolls-royce-c77e2594.html">Rolls-Royce</a> ch yu tp trung vo vic m bo cu trc ca mu xe sao cho xng vi thng hiu m ngi ta thng v von xe chy m nh mt tm thm ma thut ca cng ty, trong khi vn m m bo c  bn cn thit v p ng c nhng iu kin thi tit v cng khc nghit.</p><p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-0" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-0" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452075707-1452066947-1.jpg" alt="L Rolls-Royce Phantom dng nn tng khung nhm mi - 1" /></span></p><p align="center">Nn tng khung nhm mi c Rolls-Royce th nghim trn mu Phantom v ngy trang kn mt</p><p>Pha cng ty t chi tit l nhng chi tit c th, nhng cu trc v nn tng ban u ca xe  tng xut hin vo u nm 2015. y l nn tng mi u tin m theo Rolls-Royce s c rt nhiu iu c bit, s sang trng bc nht, v c mc ch.</p><p>Khi tung ra th trng, chic off-road ny s c t tn l Cullinan, l tn mt vin kim cng th ln nht th gii c tm thy cho n nay. Chic SUV c ch to bng nhm  gi trng lng nh cho xe v pht trin trn h khung gm c cu trc hon ton mi cha c s dng cho bt k mu no.</p><p>Gim c iu hnh ca <em>Rolls-Royce</em>, ng Torsen Muller-Otvos chia s :"By gi l thi im  thc hin bc tip theo trong k hoch pht trin nhng mu xe sang trng nht ca hng. y l l do ti sao ti cng b vic th nghim mt kt cu c quyn hon ton mi ca Rolls-Royce  chnh thc c bt u. Kin trc mi ny l minh chng cho s u t ca Rolls-Royce cho vic pht trin nhng mu xe tng lai ca hng.</p><p>Trc , Bentley  gia nhp th trng SUV vi chic Bentayga v khng nh y l model sang trng nht trong phn khc ny, nhng CEO Rolls-Royce Torsten Muller Otvos p tr li rng Bentley SUV r rng ng  v tr th 2 v Rolls-Royce s chim v tr qun qun khi tung ra bn  i l vo cui nm 2018. Khi c hi liu Rolls-Royce s gi tn gi Cullinan hay khng, ng Muller ni rng ng thch ci tn ny, c ngha l chic SUV nhiu kh nng s ly tn theo vin kim cng th ln nht th gii.</p><p>Nhng thng s k thut ca chic xe vn bt v m tn, nhng mt s bo co trc  ni rng chic SUV siu sang ny s trang b ng c V12 6.75 lt. Ngoi ra, m hnh ny cng c n on s vay mn mt s thnh phn t ngi anh em BMW X7.</p>', 'L Rolls-Royce Phantom dng nn tng khung nhm mi', 'Mt mu Phantom ang c Rolls-Royce th nghim da trn nn tng khung nhm mi, v s p dng cho tt c cc mu xe ca hng t 2018.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '281-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:00:47', '2016-01-07 03:00:47', '', 281, 'http://localhost/tmdt/uncategorized/281-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(287, 1, '2016-01-07 03:02:16', '2016-01-07 03:02:16', 'Mc d c xut thn kh khim tn trong mt khu vc dnh cho giai cp cng nhn  B o Nha, b l mt ngi lm vn theo thi v, m l mt u bp. Tuy nhin, bng ti nng v s n lc khng ngng ngh, Cristiano Ronaldo - cu th thuc bin ch Real Madrid ang l mt trong nhng cu th v i nht ca lng <a class="TextlinkBaiviet" title="bng " href="http://www.24h.com.vn/bong-da-c48.html">bng </a> th gii.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-0" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-0" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-11.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 1" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Ronaldo l mt trong nhng cu th bng  s hu nhiu x hp khng nht</p>\r\nC th ni, bng   ngm su vo trong mu ca i trng tuyn quc gia B o Nha, ngay t khi cn nh cu  lm quen vi tri bng v b hc cng v tnh yu vi tri bng. Ln 8 tui, Ronaldo tham gia i bng u tin  Andorinha. Ln 9 tui CR7 k hp ng u tin vi i bng Nacional, trc khi chuyn ti i bng chuyn nghip Sporting vo nm 2001.\r\n\r\nS nghip ca Ronaldo bt u n r khi chng trai bc vo tui 16, vi k nng chi bng ngy cng hon thin, anh c CLB ln nht th gii l Manchester United k hp ng vi gi 12 triu bng.\r\n\r\nKhng lu sau danh ting ca cu th ngi B c khng nh trong lng tc cu, khi ti trn chung kt cp FA nm 2004, Ronaldo  ghi c 3 bn thng v gip MU ot chc v ch nm . Nm 2008, Ronaldo tip tc c Manchester United k hp ng ln ti 31 triu bng trong 5 nm.\r\n\r\nTr thnh tr ct ti MU, v nhn mc lng hu hnh nhng lc ny CR7 li cm thy khng vui, cng trong nm 2008 anh vn tip tc c nhng ng gp to ln cho i bng khi a MU v ch UEFA Champions League nm 2008, c nhn anh m lun danh hiu cu th xut sc nht nm ca FIFA.\r\n\r\nNm 2009, Real Madrid  a Cristiano Ronaldo v sn Santiago Bernabeu t Man United vi gi 131 triu USD  ph v mi k lc chuyn nhng lc by gi, bin anh thnh cu th t gi nht hnh tinh.\r\n\r\nTi Real, Ronaldo tr thnh cu th c mc lng cao nht CLB cng nh lng bng , vi mc lng sau thu 20 triu Euro/nm. Ngoi ra, anh cng l tn tui t gi cho cc nhn hng ni ting, thu v hng chc triu USD mi nm. Chnh v vy, CR7 c c s  u t cho s thch ca mnh l tu siu xe.\r\n\r\nDi y l 10 chic siu xe tuyt nht trong hng chc chic xe khc ca Cristiano Ronaldo.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>10. Porsche 911 Carrera S Cabriolet 2013</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-1" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-1" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-10.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 2" /></span></p>\r\nPorsche 911 l chic xe xp cui trong bng danh sch nhng <strong>siu xe ca Ronaldo</strong>. Tuy nhin, n cng l nim m c ca hng triu ngi. Chic xe th thao vi ng c t pha sau s hu cng sut 420 m lc ti 6500 vng/pht.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>9. Bentley Continental GT Speed 2006</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-2" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-2" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-9.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 3" /></span></p>\r\n thi im ngi sao ngi B s hu chic Bentley Continental GT, n l mt trong nhng chic Bentley mnh nht m hng xe Anh quc s hu. Chic xe s hu ng c mnh m t cng sut 626 m lc, m men xon 650 lb-ft, ni tht xa hoa, v tng tc t 0-96 km/gi ch trong 4 giy. Mc d s hu tc  cao, nhng chic Continental GT  c tnh ton k lng  mi ln vo cua c mt m v an ton hn.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>8. Ferrari 599 GTB Fiorano 2006</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-3" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-3" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-8.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 4" /></span></p>\r\nMc d chic Ferrari 599 GTB Fiorano khng cn nm trong garage ca Ronaldo sau ln tai nn ti mt ng hm gn sn bay Manchester, nhng c mt thc t khng th ph nhn n l mt tuyt tc.\r\n\r\nFerrari 599 GTB Fiorano c trang b ng c sn sinh cng sut 620 m lc ti 7.600 vng/pht v t theo chiu dc mang li tnh thm m rt cao.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>7. Bentley Continental GTC 2006</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-4" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-4" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-7.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 5" /></span></p>\r\nVi chic Bentley th 2 trong garage, c th thy siu sao ca CLB Real cng l mt tn  ca hng xe Anh quc. Mu xe hai ca c trang b ng c cng sut 552 m lc, c th tng vn tc t 0 n 100km/h trong vng 4,8 giy. Tc  ti a ca Bentley Continental GTC ln ti 318km/h. Mc gi ca chic siu xe ny ri vo khong 200 nghn  la.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>6. Aston Martin DB9 2013</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-5" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-5" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-6.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 6" /></span></p>\r\nMt tuyt tc ch thc ca hng xe Anh, Aston Martin DB9 cn l mt trong nhng chic xe c yu thch nht trong lng siu xe, do , s khng ly lm ngc nhin khi <em>Ronaldo</em>  tu mt chic vo trong b su tp  s ca mnh.\r\n\r\nAston Martin DB9 2013 khng ch gy n tng nh ni tht cao cp v kh nng tng tc t 0-100km/gi ch trong 4,6 giy, cng sut ti a 510 m lc.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>5. Rolls Royce Phantom Drophead Coupe 2007</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-6" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-6" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-5.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 7" /></span></p>\r\nNu bn mun tr nn sang trng v c mi ngi ch , ch cn tu cho mnh chic Phantom Drophead Coupe. ng c cng sut 453 m lc, mc gi trn tri khng phi l im nhn trn chic xe siu sang ny.\r\n\r\nim nhn nm  thit k th cng sang trng bc nht lng x hp, cng cm hng t du thuyn J-class nhng nm 1930, phn mui bng g trn Phantom Drophead Coup l s kt hp hon ho gia nt p truyn thng ca Rolls-Royce v k ngh cao ca cc k s Rolls-Royce.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>4. Maserati GranTurismo 2009</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-7" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-7" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-4.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 8" /></span></p>\r\nKhng phi l m hnh mnh m nht trong danh sch nhng <u>siu xe m CR7 s hu</u>, nhng Maserati GranTurismo vn c siu sao bng  ny c bit yu thch.\r\n\r\nMc d ch s hu cng sut 400 m lc ti 7.100 vng/pht, nhng Maserati GranTurismo vn to cho ngi iu khin mt cm gic thoi mi, mt m khi chy vi tc c cao.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>3. Audi R8 2010</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-8" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-8" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-3.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 9" width="500" /></span></p>\r\nSiu xe Audi R8 5.2 FSI l sn phm m Ronaldo v cc ng i ti Real Madrid c hng xe Audi tng. y l chng trnh hp tc  qung b hnh nh gia hng xe c v CLB Hong gia Ty Ban Nha.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>2. BMW M6 2006</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-9" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-9" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-2.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 10" /></span></p>\r\nBMW M6 cng c xem l mu xe c sc hp dn nht hin nay. Chic xe khng thiu bt k trang thit b hin i no trong ngnh cng nghip  t. T h thng bn  dn ng navigation th h mi ca BMW, ni tht da Merino cao cp, gh massage, h thng m thanh Bang &amp; Olufsen vi 16 loa, chc nng hin th thng tin trn knh li Head-up Display, chc nng cnh bo im m, cnh bo chch ln ng, b phanh gm carbon hiu nng cao v gi trang b Competition Package gip tng cng sut thm 15 m lc (a tng cng sut ca xe ln 575 m lc), tinh chnh li tay li v phuc.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>1. Audi RS6 2003</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-10" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-10" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-01/1451629536-1451628931-1.jpg" alt="10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo - 11" /></span></p>\r\nKhng phi l phin bn tuyt nh trong garage ca ng kim Qu bng vng th gii, nhng vn c nhng iu m chng ta khng th khng ngng m chic Audi RS6 2003 ny. Nh c h dn ng 4 bnh m chic xe c th tng tc t 0-96km/gi ch trong 3,7 giy, cng sut ti a 450 m lc.', '10 siu xe cc nh ca Cristiano Ronaldo', 'Bng  khng ch mang n cho Ronaldo nim am m, s ni ting, giu c m cn l bn p  ngi sao ny s hu nhng siu xe danh ting bc nht lng x hp.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '10-sieu-xe-cuc-dinh-cua-cristiano-ronaldo', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:02:16', '2016-01-07 03:02:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=287', 0, 'post', '', 0);
