(298, 1, '2016-01-07 03:17:44', '2016-01-07 03:17:44', 'D c ni dung kh nhm nhng <em>Thi t phi thng chc k</em> vn tr thnh phim hot nht trn sng truyn hnh Trung Quc trong nhng ngy qua. B phim c nhiu m n, soi ca tr p gy st cng lot cnh nng nh vo th hiu ca ngi xem.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , nhng trang phc c khi l lng, h hang, lc nhi hng hiu ba bi ca b phim ang tr thnh  ti bn tn si ni ca cng ng mng.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-0" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-0" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-1-0-1451891628598.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 1" /></span></p>\r\nCung tn m n trong phim Thi t phi thng chc k c gu <a class="TextlinkBaiviet" title="thi trang" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/thoi-trang-c78.html">thi trang</a> "mt m" v gy tranh ci\r\n\r\n<strong>Trang phc h hang n l lng</strong>\r\n\r\nD l mt b phim c trang nhng trang phc ca cc cung tn, m n trong b phim ny li v cng mt m vi nhng phn x t, khoe vai trn gi cm. Gii thch v iu ny, o din L Ho Ct Ct tng cho bit, do thi im quay phim (thng 8 va qua) qu nng nn trang phc ca din vin phi ti gin v thoi mi nht.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , cng theo ng, vic trang phc s si v c phn rt u b cho l do kinh ph khng nhiu, thi gian eo hp. Theo mt ngun tin Trung Quc, hu ht trang phc u c may t vi mua  ch hay mua trn trang bn hng Taobao.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-1" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-