(299, 1, '2016-01-07 03:25:59', '2016-01-07 03:25:59', '<h1>PH THNG GIA SNG THN</h1>\r\nKhu "Ph Thng Gia Sng Thn", nm trn mng li giao thng tin li, nt tht giao thng t vng xoay An Ph, ng t Nm Nm Mi v Trung tm hnh chnh D An.\r\n\r\n<b><strong>Ph Thng Gia Sng Thn D An Bnh Dng</strong></b>\r\n\r\nTa lc ngay Trung Tm KCN Sng Thn - Trung Tm Hnh Chnh D An. Ni xc nh l khu phc hp Dch v - Thng mi Trung tm tnh Bnh Dng.\r\n\r\nKhu "Ph Thng Gia Sng Thn", nm trn mng li giao thng tin li, nt tht giao thng t vng xoay An Ph, ng t Nm Nm Mi v Trung tm hnh chnh D An.\r\n\r\n-Mt ng 743A ni lin gia KCN VSIP 1 vi tuyn ng Quc L 1.\r\n\r\n-Ngay tuyn ng cao tc M Phc  Tn Vn, KCN M Phc  KCN Vsip 2 - KCN Vsip 1  KCN Sng Thn\r\n\r\n-Nm gia sng Si Gn v sng ng Nai d dng di chuyn ng thy qua cc khu vc khc.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><strong>Quy m d n</strong></b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Din tch d n: 10.000m2.</li>\r\n	<li>Ch u t<b><strong>:</strong></b>Cng Ty TNHH Quc Thi Thnh</li>\r\n	<li>n v thit k: Cng Ty TNHH T Vn Xy Dng Ph Cng</li>\r\n	<li>Tip th v phn phi c quyn<b><strong>:</strong></b><b><strong>Cng Ty C Phn Dch V Xy Dng a c t Ngun.</strong></b></li>\r\n	<li>Tin : ng ni b rng 8m, mt ng nha hon ton, h thng in, nc y , va h rng...Mt ng l T 743A</li>\r\n	<li>M bn giai on 1: 100 nn, din tch 75  200m2</li>\r\n	<li>Thanh ton linh hot - Ngn hng VietinBank cam kt h tr vay 70% gi tr t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nD n c cp php xy dng 1/500 ca Th x D An tnh Bnh Dng, trong giai on 1 m bn ch 100 nn, S hng ring th c 100%, tng din tch 10.000m2. Khu Ph Thng Mi c quy hoch theo tiu chun quc t, vi kin trc khong t c thit k trang nh hin i ph hp vi doanh nhn.\r\n\r\nKhu Ph Thng Gia Sng Thn c hnh thnh  pht trin thnh Khu Ph Thng Mi  Dch V ln nht KCN Sng Thn, tr thnh mt Khu Ph Thng Mi tiu biu cho ng Nam B. ng thi, khi sng v lm vic ti y cc thng gia s pht trin doanh nghip, cng ty mt cch ti a v c sng trong mi trng chuyn nghip, tip xc v hc hi kinh nghim t nhng thng gia thnh t.\r\n\r\nD n nm ngay trung tm