(303, 1, '2016-01-07 03:27:58', '2016-01-07 03:27:58', '<div class="short">y l nhn nh c CBRE Vit Nam a ra hm nay (5/1), ng thi cng b bo co th trng bt ng sn TP.HCM qu IV/2015.</div>\r\n<div class="full">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://static.bizlive.vn/uploaded/dinhthom/2016_01_05/anh1_xrkh.jpg?width=670&amp;height=350&amp;crop=auto&amp;scale=both" alt="" width="600" height="313" />\r\n\r\nTh trng nh  phc hi n tng trong nm qua v k vng s bng n trong nm 2016. nh: Ngn Dn.\r\n\r\nTheo CBRE, lm pht thp - trung bnh ch tng 0,63% trong nm 2015 - l nhn t quan trng gip kch thch tiu dng v u t tng mnh trong nm 2015, trong  c th trng bt ng sn.\r\n\r\nTng t, li sut cho vay mua nh thp cng gip cc hot ng giao dch trong th trng bt ng sn si ni hn trong nm nay. T trng cho vay bt ng sn chim 8% tng d n ca nn kinh t trong nm 2015, d bo con s ny s tng 15 - 20% trong nm 2016.\r\n\r\n<strong>Nh  bng n</strong>\r\n\r\nTheo CBRE Vit Nam, nm 2015 nh du s phc hi mnh m ca th trng nh  khi ngun cung cho bn tng mnh. Lng tiu th rt kh quan, gi bn cng c ci thin v hp l hn, c bit l phn khc trung v cao cp.\r\n\r\nTi TP.HCM, c nm qua, th trng  cho n ti 41.787 cn h t 78 d n, a s tp trung  pha ng (47%) v pha Nam (27%) ca thnh ph, tng ti 122% so vi nm 2014. Nm 2015 cng l nm ghi nhn lng cn h cho bn mi nhiu nht nh ngun cung t mt s d n ln nh Vinhomes Central Park (Bnh Thnh), Masteri Tho in (qun 2)...\r\n\r\nS liu t CBRE cho bit, nm 2015 khp li vi tng lng giao dch cao nht lch s trong mt nm. C th, c tnh  tiu th 36.160 cn h, tng ti 98% so vi nm 2014. Con s ny bao gm giao dch bn l cho ngi mua l v c giao dch bn s cho cc nh u t, t chc v cc i l mi gii bt ng sn.\r\n\r\nCh ring trong qu IV/2015, c tnh tng lng giao dch trn th trng TP.HCM khong trn 10.300 cn h (tng 28% so vi qu III i vi giao dch bn l) v trn 8.100 cn (tng nh 2% so qu III i vi giao dch bn s).\r\n\r\nng lu , nu xt v t trng trong lng giao dch, nhng d n trung v cao cp, vi gi bn dao ng trong khong t 1,3 - 5 t ng/cn, bn rt chy, chim hn 75% tng lng giao dch ton TP.HCM trong nm 2015.\r\n\r\nTrong khi giai on 2009 - 2014, cn h bnh dn c gi di 1,3 t ng/cn lun lun dn u v t l giao dch thnh cng. iu ny cho thy, hin nay, th trng ang dn c s chuyn bin v ngi mua c xu hng chung nhng sn phm cao cp hn.\r\n\r\nTrong nm 2015, gi bn trn ton th trng s cp t trung bnh 2.012 USD/m2, tng 4,4% so vi nm trc v 2,5% so vi qu trc. c bit, gi bn ca phn khc cao cp tng vt (tng 8,3% so vi cng k nm trc) v hin  mc trung bnh 2.025 USD/m2. C bit mt s d n c v tr p, ch u t uy tn  mnh dn tng gi t 10 - 15%.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://static.bizlive.vn/uploaded/dinhthom/2016_01_05/anh2_xoit.jpg?width=670" alt="" width="600" height="313" />\r\n\r\nVn phng hng A ti TP.HCM s bt u si ng tr li trong nm 2016? nh: Ngn Dn.\r\n\r\nB Dng Thy Dung, Gim c B phn Nghin cu v t vn CBRE Vit Nam tit l: "Mc d gi cao, cc d n cao cp vn c tiu th mnh v cc hot ng m bn vn ang din ra nhn nhp. iu  chng t th trng  bc vo chu k mi".\r\n\r\nTheo CBRE, trong nm 2016, d kin TP.HCM s cho n hn 45.000 cn h t 90 d n thuc mi phn khc. Trong , t trng cc d n cao cp v hng sang s tip tc tng thm khong 20% so vi nm 2015.\r\n\r\nTrc  bng n ca th trng nh , nhiu chuyn gia cng lu  v nhng kha cnh ri ro ca th trng nh cung sn phm cao cp c nguy c vt cu, gi bn b y ln qu cao, gia tng giao dch o...\r\n\r\nng Marc Townsend, Tng gim c iu hnh CBRE Vit Nam cnh bo: "Khi th trng tng trng qu nhanh, qu nng th nguy c trt ng ray lun lun hin hu. Cc nh u t cn trang b y  kin thc v kinh nghim  thch ng vi cuc cnh tranh ngy cng khc lit hn".\r\n\r\n<strong>Vn phng khan him</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong khi th trng nh  ang trn  phc hi n tng th tri li, th trng vn phng c phn "lp v" hn. Ti TP.HCM, trong qu 4/2015 hon ton khng c ngun cung mi vn phng hng A no c tung ra th trng.\r\n\r\nDo yu t khan him ca vn phng hng A  khin gi cho thu ca th trng ny tng nh. C th, ti TP.HCM, gi thu hng A tng 1,5%, gi thu hng B cng tng nhng cha nhiu do ch u t c gng duy tr mc gi thu n nh  tng kh nng cnh tranh v lp y nhng ta nh cn trng.\r\n\r\nTuy nhin, theo gii phn tch, nh nhng tn hiu tch cc nh dng vn FDI tng mnh, tc  tng trng GDP n nh, Hip nh TPP c thng qua v s hnh thnh ca Cng ng kinh t ASEAN (AEC)  to ra tm l tch cc cho th trng vn phng. iu ny c nhn thy r rng khi t l trng hng A v c hng B u gim nh.\r\n\r\nTheo CBRE, nhm 5 i tng khch hng c nhu cu thu cao nht ln lt l: cng ngh thng tin/in t, sn xut, ti chnh/ngn hng, t vn v hu cn.\r\n\r\nNhm p ng ngun cung khi vn phng hng A ang khan him, cc chuyn gia cho rng th trng ny ang bt u nhen nhm phc hi tr li v ngun cung s tng trong thi gian ti. C th, nh BizLIVE  thng tin, ta nh Saigon One Tower ang c ti khi ng s l ngun cung hng A quan trng ti TP.HCM trong thi gian ti.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Th trng bt ng sn hng li t s phc hi kinh t', 'y l nhn nh c CBRE Vit Nam a ra hm nay (5/1), ng thi cng b bo co th trng bt ng sn TP.HCM qu IV/2015.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '302-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:27:58', '2016-01-07 03:27:58', '', 302, 'http://localhost/tmdt/uncategorized/302-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(304, 1, '2016-01-07 03:29:06', '2016-01-07 03:29:06', '<div class="short">Cng v cui nm, phn khc t nn, nh ph ti th trng bt ng sn pha Nam, cng si ng vi hng lot d n m bn, n ma cao im giao dch.</div>\r\n<div class="full">\r\n\r\nTi TP.HCM, khc vi cn h tng cung t bin, phn khc t nn vn gi ngun cung kh n nh v thanh khon tt. Tp on Kin , va cng b m bn t 2, d n nh ph bit lp Citibella (Q.2), sau khi giao dch thnh cng 85/105 t 1. Trc , Khang in cng  m bn khu nh ph, bit th bit lp Melosa Garden (Q.9). Cng ty C phn a c Vn Xun m bn d n Vn Xun Bc Si Gn (Q.12) v d n Vn Xun An Lc (Q.G Vp).\r\n\r\nMt s d n khc cng chun b ra hng nh Jamona Golden Silk (Q.7), Him Lam Ph An gn i l Phm Vn ng (Q.Th c), Camellia Garden (Q.7)\r\n\r\n<img src="http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2015/12/22/09/20151222091558-dat-nen-nha-pho.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="336" />\r\n\r\n<em>Mi gii trn ra cc d n ven khu cng nghip  n khch</em>\r\n\r\nTheo ng Trn Khnh Quang, Tng Gim c Cng ty T vn u t Bt ng sn Vit An Ha, phn khc t nn, nh ph c kh nhiu nh u t tm kim v tnh an ton v kh nng gia tng gi tr bn vng. Tuy nhin, khch hng cn thn trng v php l v nhiu d n tranh th th trng st, chy ua m bn khi cha  iu kin. Thm ch nhiu doanh nghip khng tn tui cn phn l c t nng nghip  bn.\r\n\r\nTi Ca Lp, Vng Tu, d n Khu  th ph bin Marine City cng  c Sn giao dch BS Hng Hng Thnh m bn t 2 vi cam kt li nhun 12%/nm. Hin khu vc ny vn cha c nhiu d n m bn v ang cn ch hon thin php l.\r\n\r\nt nn ven cc khu cng nghip cng si ng tr li, c bit sau thng tin Vit Nam m phn thnh cng Hip nh i tc Xuyn Thi Bnh Dng (TPP). nh gi tc ng ca TPP vi th trng bt ng sn Vit Nam, CBRE cho rng t cng nghip, kho bi, hu cn vn ti, vn phng v nh  l nhng lnh vc chu tc ng ch yu.\r\n\r\nTheo ng Trn Minh Nht, Tng Gim c Times Housing Corporation, c hch v ngun vn u t vo cc khu cng nghip sau TPP, chnh l yu t m nhiu d n ven khu cng nghip  Bnh Dng, Long An ang k vng  n theo.\r\n\r\nD n Khu  Th TM - DV Ct Tng Ph Nguyn, gn cc khu cng ngh cao nh Hong Gia, Xuyn , khu cng nghip c Ha (Long An), ch mi cng b mt thi gian ngn  c hn 90% sn phm cho bn c ch. Trc , Phc Khang Corporation cng  bn sch d n Lng Sen Vit Nam ti Long An.\r\n\r\nTi Bnh Dng, d n ph thng mi G.Cape Town, mt tin Vnh ai 4, i din khu cng nghip VSIP 2, va m bn, cng ghi nhn thanh khon tch cc. Nhiu c t cng gom nn ti nh c xung quanh  bn li kim chnh lch.\r\n\r\nng Hong Anh Tun, Tng Gim c Tng Cng ty Tc t Tc Vng, cho rng: Bnh Dng l tnh c sn lng, mt  tp trung khu cng nghip v thu ht vn FDI ln ca c nc. Do vy, khu vc ny chc chn s hng li n, li kp t TPP.\r\n\r\nCng theo ng Tun, Lut Nh  c hiu lc t ngy 1/7/2015 vi nhng quy nh thng thong cho Vit kiu mua nh ti l c hi thu ht kiu hi chy vo bt ng sn, c bit l giai on cui nm.\r\n\r\nD ghi nhn nhiu im tch cc, nhng theo nhiu chuyn gia, ch nhng d n v tr c a th mi c tim nng gia tng gi tr. c bit, cn lu  d n phi hon thin v php l, trnh ri ro t vic phn l bn nn tri php  tng xy ra trong nhng cn st trc y ti Bnh Dng.\r\n\r\n</div>', 't nn, nh ph tng tc n dng tin cui nm', 'Cng v cui nm, phn khc t nn, nh ph ti th trng bt ng sn pha Nam, cng si ng vi hng lot d n m bn, n ma cao im giao dch.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dat-nen-nha-pho-tang-toc-don-dong-tien-cuoi-nam', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:29:06', '2016-01-07 03:29:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=304', 0, 'post', '', 0),
