(306, 1, '2016-01-07 03:30:07', '2016-01-07 03:30:07', '<div class="short">Hot ng mua bn, sp nhp cc doanh nghip, d n trong lnh vc bt ng sn din ra kh si ng trong nm 2015. Cc ng ln a c vn ang th hin c sc mnh ti chnh.</div>\r\n<div class="full">\r\n\r\n<a href="http://datnguon.com.vn/"><img src="http://cafef.vcmedia.vn/thumb_w/660/2015/diamond-1450426217284.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="377" /></a>\r\n\r\nTm tt\r\n\r\n-Nhng ci tn nh Vingroup, Novaland, VID Group, Keppel Land, Lottevn ang chim lnh trn th trng trong hot ng mua bn, sp nhp doanh nghip (M&amp;A) bt ng sn.\r\n\r\n-Thng v nh m nht c th k ti nh d n StarCity Centre v tay Vingroup, Celadon City v tay Gamuda, Chow Tai Fook thu tm Casino Nam Hi An,\r\n\r\nTheo ghi nhn ca chng ti, nm qua nhng cuc i ch ti d n bt ng sn din ra kh mnh. Trong , kh nhiu d n ln tn tui  c ch mi nh Casino Nam Hi An, StarCity Centre, CeladonCity, Indochina Plaza Hanoi, Daimond Plaza, Hyatt Regency Danang,\r\n\r\nBn cnh , nhm chun b cho qu trnh m rng u t, chim lnh th trng nhiu ng ln BS cn tp trung vo chin lc mua c phn chi phi  nhng doanh nghip c qu t ln, t vng qua cc t IPO.\r\n\r\nNhng thng v nh m nht 2015\r\n\r\n<strong>1.StarCity Centre v tay Vingroup</strong>\r\n\r\nKhu t c quy m rng khong 5ha nm gc ng t mt ng Trn Duy Hng v Khut Duy Tin. Mt v tr vng trung tm Th , khu t vnh khn ny t nm 2008  c lp d n  lm i ng cho d n xy dng bo tng H Ni tr gi 2.300 t ng. Nm 2013, Ocean Group v Vinaconex c giao t  trin khai d n ny, gm c chung c cao cp, thng mi, vn phng, khch sn\r\n\r\nTuy nhin, do gp bin c nn Ocean Group buc phi chuyn nhng d n ny cho i tc khc. Nm 2015, Vingroup  chnh thc mua li d n ny thng qua cng ty thnh vin l Vincom Retail. c bit, sau khi hon tt th tc, Vincom Reatail s hu ti 90% c phn ch u t d n ny.\r\n\r\n<strong>2.T ph Hng Kng ng ch mi d n Casino Nam Hi An</strong>\r\n\r\ny l mt trong nhng d n ln nht khu vc min Trung, c s quan tm ca cc tp on a quc gia quy m ti 4 t USD. Giai on 1 ca D n, bao gm pht trin khu ngh dng kt hp khu vui chi c thng, sn golf, khu bit th v cn h cao cp vi tng vn u t hn 500 triu USD.\r\n\r\nMi y, VinaCapital  xc nhn khng cn l c ng chnh ca cng ty qun l d n v thay vo  l tp on Chow Tai Fook (Hng Kng). Tuy nhin, cng ty ny vn nm gi 22,55% vi vai tr l c ng chin lc.\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Gaw Capital Partners thu tm nhiu d n ti Vit Nam</strong>\r\n\r\ny l tp on n t nc Anh, hin tp on ny ang gia tng thu tm BS  khu vc Chu -Thi Bnh Dng, tng ti sn ca qu u t ny c cho l khong hn 9 t USD. Nm 2015, Gaw Capital Partners y mnh thu tm cc d n  Vit Nam.\r\n\r\nin hnh l thng v mua li 4 d n gm Hyatt Regency Danang ( Nng), Indochina Plaza Hanoi, Malibu Villas (Qung Nam) v TP.HCM (Park City). Gi tr thng v ny c cho l 106 triu USD.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , tp on ny cn hp tc vi 2 i tc khc ca Vit Nam  xy dng t hp Empire City c tng mc u t 1,2 t USD ti Th Thim (Tp.HCM), vi t l 50-50. Trong , ng ch  c d n ta nh quan st cao 86 tng.\r\n\r\n<strong>4. Celadon City v tay Gamuda Land</strong>\r\n\r\nD n Celadon City c tng din tch hn 82,5 ha, c v tr ti phng Sn K, qun Tn Ph, Tp.HCM vi tng mc u t d kin ban u khong 24.758 t ng. Ban u do Sacomreal l ch u t.\r\n\r\nTrong nm 2015, cc i tc  hon tt thng v chuyn nhng d n ny cho Gamuda Land, vi gi tr hp ng chuyn nhng 40% c phn (tng ng 64,1 triu USD) trong d n Celadon City.\r\n\r\n<strong>5. C mp Novaland hi sinh d n cht</strong>\r\n\r\nNm 2007 ch t mt d n chung c cao cp Sunrise City ti qun 7, nhng n nay thng qua chin lc M&amp;A, Novaland  nng s d n m mnh s hu ln con s 25. c bit l trong nm 2015 tp on ny  thu tm mt lot d n.\r\n\r\nC ti 2/3 trong s 25 d n ny ang trong giai on thi cng. Cc d n mi nh Sunrise Cityview, Sunrise Riverside, Golden Mansion, Newton Residence, The Park View, Duxton Residence. VinaCapital  rt vo Novaland mt khon vn gn 50 triu USD thng qua vic pht hnh tri phiu chuyn i.\r\n\r\n<strong>6. Diamond Plaza v tay Lotte</strong>\r\n\r\nTp on Lotte  mua ti 70% c phn ca ta cao c Diamond Plaza, Tp.HCM. Theo , Lotte s nm quyn iu hnh to nh ny t mt doanh nghip Hn Quc khc l Posco. Tuy nhin, gi tr thng v ny khng c tit l.\r\n\r\nDiamond Plaza l ta cao c gm 22 tng, bao gm k c hai tng hm, c khnh thnh t thng 8/2000. Cng trnh ny c vn u t ban u khong 60 triu USD.\r\n\r\n<strong>7. Keppel Land thu tm H Ni Westgate</strong>\r\n\r\nKhu  th ny c v tr trn ng i l Thng Long thuc Quc Oai, H Ni. Trong nm, Gami Group  bn 60% cho Keppel Land  hp tc pht trin d n ny, d kin c tng vn u t trn 100 triu USD, trong  Keppel Land d kin nm gi 60% c phn.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, Keppel Land  m rng danh mc d n bng cch mua li d n pht trin nh  ca cng ty Tin Phc vi gi 26,7 triu USD.\r\n\r\nt vng v tay ng ln qua cc cuc IPO\r\n\r\nTrong nm 2015, con sng ngm thu tm t vng din ra mnh m. Trong  ni ln l cc tp on t nhn ln ca Vit Nam nh Vingroup, VID Group, Novaland, BRG,u t ra qu mnh.\r\n\r\nNi bt nh Vingroup v VID Group (nay l TNG Holdings) u tr thnh c ng chin lc ca Vinatex , ln lt s hu 10% v 14%; BRG cn l c ng chin lc nm 43% ti OSC Vit Nam, nm 27%  Thng Long GTC, nm 46% ti Intimex; nhm nh u t Novaland nm gi khong 50% c phn ti Cng sng Tp.HCM (Casoco)\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Nhng thng v M&A bt ng sn nh m nht 2015', 'Hot ng mua bn, sp nhp cc doanh nghip, d n trong lnh vc bt ng sn din ra kh si ng trong nm 2015. Cc ng ln a c vn ang th hin c sc mnh ti chnh.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nhung-thuong-vu-ma-bat-dong-san-dinh-dam-nhat-2015', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:30:07', '2016-01-07 03:30:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=306', 0, 'post', '', 0),
