(308, 1, '2016-01-07 03:31:11', '2016-01-07 03:31:11', '<div class="short">Kt thc nm 2015, th trng BS vn mi mit nhng phin ch vt  chy  cho nm 2016 ha hn nhiu trin vng v thanh khon, gi tr tng trng. Bc tranh a c nm qua, theo gc nhn qun l, c khc ha qua mt s chnh sch  quyt ngh mang tnh khc phc cc s c in hnh.</div>\r\n<div class="full">\r\n\r\nT vn  m bo cuc sng cho ngi dn trong chung c, cht lng cc cng trnh nh  cao tng ti cu chuyn m bo tun th php lut bn hng BS. D bo, BS 2016 s tr nn minh bch, DN s nghim chnh chp hnh lut nh, khch hng yn tm giao dch nh hiu qu ca cy gy qun l.\r\n\r\n<strong>Chy nh, nh qun l c mt!</strong>\r\n\r\nC th ni, ha hon ti chung c thng mi cao tng  tr thnh s c mang tnh xuyn sut (v thi gian) v c th (v nguyn nhn c bn) trong nm 2015. T kha chy chung c ph bin ti mc, ch cn trong 0,55 giy, cng c google tr v 706.000 kt qu.\r\n\r\nH Ni c nhc ti ch yu xoay quanh s c chp in gy chy  chung c Xa La (H ng), Vimeco (Cu Giy), ha hon  tng 18 chung c cao cp H Gm Plaza\r\n\r\nTi qu IV/2015, phn khc nh  thng mi gi r v ngay c mt phn d n cao cp bt u gp kh (thm ch phi bn r, ct l su nh mt s h phn d n ca X nghip Lai Chu ti qun Hong Mai)  thot hng.\r\n\r\nKhng ch hiu nng phng chy  cha chy  chung c bnh dn a phn ch l hnh thc, nhng chung c thng mi cao cp nh m nh d n ca May H Gm hay Vimeco Phm Hng ca cng ty CP Vimeco cng chng kh hn\r\n\r\nKhc chng, sai phm  nguyn nhn ca ha hon  d n gi r mang tnh h thng v nng n hn so vi phn cn li. Du vy, s vo cuc mang tnh chin lc, x l t gc ca nh chc trch  mang li tnh nghim minh, cng bng ca php lut BS.\r\n\r\nC th, thng 12, H Ni ng  vi  xut ca Cnh st PCCC thnh ph dng xem xt vic giao ch u t, cp php u t i vi cc d n mi trn a bn cho DN t nhn xy dng s 1 tnh in Bin.\r\n\r\nThng 11, trc thc trng ng bo ng v tnh hnh ha hon trn c nc cng nh  nh cao tng, Ph Th tng Hong Trung Hi yu cu cc b, ngnh a phng lin quan tng kim tra cng tc PCCC, r sot, nh gi, phn loi cc khu dn c, chung c, nh cao tng, kin quyt khng nghim thu cc chung c khng m bo yu cu v PCCC  a vo hot ng. Thm ch, phi coi vn bn nghim thu v PCCC l mt trong nhng giy t bt buc khi xem xt cp chng nhn quyn s hu nh, t i vi chung c cao tng.\r\n\r\nK t thi im BS b ph bng en u c  thi gi  bn nh trn giy  tn kho km n xu, nm 2015 ghi nhn s vo cuc quyt lit ca c quan thu i vi trch nhim truy ngha v ti chnh thu ca DN ni chung v cc n v hot ng trong ngnh BS ni ring.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://thoibaokinhdoanh.vn/uploads/2016/01/03/Trang%2011%20-%20Anh%20bai%20chinh-20160103-23011329.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="360" />\r\n\r\n2016, BS s minh bch, N s nghim chnh tun th lut nh, khch hng yn tm giao dch nh hiu qu qun l\r\n\r\n<strong>S khng cn Cha Chm</strong>\r\n\r\nTi a bn H Ni, sau 7 t b Cc thu H Ni cng khai danh sch n thu, tnh n ht thng 10, cc n v thuc danh sch cng khai n thu  np ht n vo ngn sch 728 t ng. ng thi, v pha cc d n, DN s dng t, hng chc trng hp c thi im b bu vi s n tin s dng t ln ti hn 2.000 t ng.\r\n\r\nT y, khch hng v gii tho tin  c c hi  c ci nhn chn xc v kh nng ti lc thc s ca nhiu ng ln trn th trng BS (nh Handico 6, cng ty CP t vn u t Ba nh, cng ty CP HBI, ch u t d n Thng Long Yn Ha)\r\n\r\nng ch , trong hng lot tn tui mau mn hon thnh (ton b hoc nh git  PV) ngha v thu, rt nhiu trng hp ang d dang vi k hoch bn sn phm d n mc tiu.\r\n\r\nC  kin cho rng mt phn l do bo v thng hiu, cn li ch yu DN BS (ch u t) e ngi thanh khon b sa st khi mi lo khng c cp chng nhn s hu cn h giao dch ca ngi mua nh gia tng.\r\n\r\nS d nh vy l v c quan thu pht i ti hu th v ch ti p dng i vi trng hp khng hon thnh ngha v thu/c tnh chy : v hiu ha ha n DN.\r\n\r\nV pha c quan s ti, cui thng 8, UBND Tp.H Ni yu cu cc s TN&amp;MT, Ti chnh, Cc Thu Tp.H Ni; UBND cc qun, huyn, th x tng cng cc bin php qun l, m bo vic thu tin s dng t, tin thu t theo quy nh ca php lut khi Nh nc giao t, cho thu t  cc t chc, c nhn thc hin cc d n (DA) u t trn a bn thnh ph.\r\n\r\nTrong , c bit phi bo m nguyn tc thu  s tin s dng t, cc khon tin pht do chm np tin s dng t v cc khon ngha v ti chnh khc vi NSNN trc khi bn giao t, cp GCN QSD t.\r\n\r\nMt ln na, cc yu t cn ch  trc khi giao dch, nhn bn giao cn h (ca ngi mua nh) c b sung thm ch bo v ngha v thu. Km theo nhng quy nh khung p dng cho hot ng kinh doanh BS hnh thnh trong tng lai, vic phi m bo nghim thu h thng PCCC v sch php l ti chnh thu c coi thanh lc trit  cc c nhn, DN ch u t chuyn bc ngn cn di tn ti thi gian qua.\r\n\r\nT y, c hi cho gii to lp a c  nng lc chuyn mn  ti chnh cnh tranh mt cch minh bch trn th trng  rng m  nhng xu x mang tn n ng, bn hng chnh (qua cc ch u t th pht, hoc sn giao dch), thi gi to st o s khng cn t tn ti.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Th trng bt ng sn: Hai c sc mang tnh bn l', 'Kt thc nm 2015, th trng BS vn mi mit nhng phin ch vt  chy  cho nm 2016 ha hn nhiu trin vng v thanh khon, gi tr tng trng. Bc tranh a c nm qua, theo gc nhn qun l, c khc ha qua mt s chnh sch  quyt ngh mang tnh khc phc cc s c in hnh.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thi-truong-bat-dong-san-hai-cu-soc-mang-tinh-ban-le', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:31:11', '2016-01-07 03:31:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=308', 0, 'post', '', 0);
