Thm ch, phi coi vn bn nghim thu v PCCC l mt trong nhng giy t bt buc khi xem xt cp chng nhn quyn s hu nh, t i vi chung c cao tng.\r\n\r\nK t thi im BS b ph bng en u c  thi gi  bn nh trn giy  tn kho km n xu, nm 2015 ghi nhn s vo cuc quyt lit ca c quan thu i vi trch nhim truy ngha v ti chnh thu ca DN ni chung v cc n v hot ng trong ngnh BS ni ring.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://thoibaokinhdoanh.vn/uploads/2016/01/03/Trang%2011%20-%20Anh%20bai%20chinh-20160103-23011329.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="360" />\r\n\r\n2016, BS s minh bch, N s nghim chnh tun th lut nh, khch hng yn tm giao dch nh hiu qu qun l\r\n\r\n<strong>S khng cn Cha Chm</strong>\r\n\r\nTi a bn H Ni, sau 7 t b Cc thu H Ni cng khai danh sch n thu, tnh n ht thng 10, cc n v thuc danh sch cng khai n thu  np ht n vo ngn sch 728 t ng. ng thi, v pha cc d n, DN s dng t, hng chc trng hp c thi im b bu vi s n tin s dng t ln ti hn 2.000 t ng.\r\n\r\nT y, khch hng v gii tho tin  c c hi  c ci nhn chn xc v kh nng ti lc thc s ca nhiu ng ln trn th trng BS (nh Handico 6, cng ty CP t vn u t Ba nh, cng ty CP HBI, ch u t d n Thng Long Yn Ha)\r\n\r\nng ch , trong hng lot tn tui mau mn hon thnh (ton b hoc nh git  PV) ngha v thu, rt nhiu trng hp ang d dang vi k hoch bn sn phm d n mc tiu.\r\n\r\nC  kin cho rng mt phn l do bo v thng hiu, cn li ch yu DN BS (ch u t) e ngi thanh khon b sa st khi mi lo khng c cp chng nhn s hu cn h giao dch ca ngi mua nh gia tng.\r\n\r\nS d nh vy l v c quan thu pht i ti hu th v ch ti p dng i vi trng hp khng hon thnh ngha v thu/c tnh chy : v hiu ha ha n DN.\r\n\r\nV pha c quan s ti, cui thng 8, UBND Tp.H Ni yu cu cc s TN&amp;MT, Ti chnh, Cc Thu Tp.H Ni; UBND cc qun, huyn, th x tng cng cc bin php qun l, m bo vic thu tin s dng t, tin thu t theo quy nh ca php lut khi Nh nc giao t, cho thu t  cc t chc, c nhn thc hin cc d n (DA) u t trn a bn thnh ph.\r\n\r\nTrong , c bit phi bo m nguyn tc thu  s tin s dng t, cc khon tin pht do chm np tin s dng t v cc khon ngha v ti chnh khc vi NSNN trc khi bn giao t, cp GCN QSD t.\r\n\r\nMt ln na, cc yu t cn ch  trc khi giao dch, nhn bn giao cn h (ca ngi mua nh) c b sung thm ch bo v ngha v thu. Km theo nhng quy nh khung p dng cho hot ng kinh doanh BS hnh thnh trong tng lai, vic phi m bo nghim thu h thng PCCC v sch php l ti chnh thu c coi thanh lc trit  cc c nhn, DN ch u t chuyn bc ngn cn di tn ti thi gian qua.\r\n\r\nT y, c hi cho gii to lp a c  nng lc chuyn mn  ti chnh cnh tranh mt cch minh bch trn th trng  rng m  nhng xu x mang tn n ng, bn hng chnh (qua cc ch u t th pht, hoc sn giao dch), thi gi to st o s khng cn t tn ti.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Th trng bt ng sn: Hai c sc mang tnh bn l', 'Kt thc nm 2015, th trng BS vn mi mit nhng phin ch vt  chy  cho nm 2016 ha hn nhiu trin vng v thanh khon, gi tr tng trng. Bc tranh a c nm qua, theo gc nhn qun l, c khc ha qua mt s chnh sch  quyt ngh mang tnh khc phc cc s c in hnh.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '308-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:31:11', '2016-01-07 03:31:11', '', 308, 'http://localhost/tmdt/uncategorized/308-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(310, 1, '2016-01-07 03:32:08', '2016-01-07 03:32:08', '<div class="short">Trong nm 2016, BS ti qun 9 s pht trin mnh mt phn l do s ci thin ca c s h tng, k n do l cc ch u t bt u dch chuyn ra khi qun 2.</div>\r\n<div class="full">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://cafef.vcmedia.vn/thumb_w/660/2016/ttsg-1451883689371.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="450" />\r\n\r\nTm tt\r\n\r\nTrong nm 2016 chng ta s chng kin th trng BS Tp.HCM si ng hn, c bit l  khu vc qun 9. i vi khu  th mi Th Thim, th trng cng s si ng hn nhng phi sau nm 2016.  cc khu vc khc nh khu pha Nam thnh ph (qun 7, Nh B, Bnh Chnh), nhiu d n mi tip tc c gii thiu vi mc gi hp l tuy nhin khu vc ny vn cn b cn tr bi h tng cha hon thin.\r\n\r\nTheo ng MacGregor, Tng Gim c iu hnh Savills Vietnam, th trng nh  ti TPHCM s n nhn ngun cung khong 16.500 cn h trong nm 2016. Nhu cu s tip tc dn dt th trng, v s phc hi s tip tc din ra trn tt c cc phn khc, t nh  cho n vn phng cho thu.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, ng MacGregor cng cho rng th trng cn c thm lc y t cc hip nh thng mi t do, vi k vng cc doanh nghip u t nc ngoi s n, ko theo nhu cu v bt ng sn. Hn th na cc nh u t Nht Bn, Hn Quc, Singapore, Hoa K cng s tng vn u t vo th trng BS Vit Nam.\r\n\r\nng MacGregor a ra d bo tip  phc hi nm 2015, chc chn trong nm 2016, chng ta s chng kin th trng BS Tp.HCM si ng hn, c bit l  khu vc qun 9. Nhiu d n  phn khc t nn/bit th/nh ph cng nh cn h ti khu vc ny cng s c a vo th trng. iu ny mt phn l do s ci thin ca c s h tng, k n do l cc ch u t bt u dch chuyn ra khi qun 2.\r\n\r\nCng theo i din Savills, i vi khu  th mi Th Thim, th trng cng s si ng hn nhng phi sau nm 2016.  cc khu vc khc nh khu pha Nam thnh ph (qun 7, Nh B, Bnh Chnh), nhiu d n mi tip tc c gii thiu vi mc gi hp l.\r\n\r\nTuy nhin, cn phi nhn nhn rng khu vc ny vn cn nhiu thch thc, ng ch  l vn  h tng. Hin ti h thng tu in ngm khu vc pha Nam cha c xy dng, khin cho giao thng s l vn  cn nhc. Nu Nh nc c th ci thin h tng  khu vc ny, nim tin ca ngi mua chc chn cng s gia tng, ng MacGregor phn tch.\r\n\r\nTheo s quan st chuyn mn ca v Tng Gim c iu hnh Savills, trong nm 2016 phn khc cn h va ti tin cng i din vi nhiu thch thc do bin  li nhun thp, cc ch u t phi xy dng vi s lng ln cn h  c th thu c li nhun. Hn na, dng sn phm ny cng ang c nhiu doanh nghip tham gia nn mc  cnh tranh ngy mt gay gt hn.\r\n\r\nCng theo MacGregor, nm 2015, th trng chng kin nhiu d n nh  thuc phn khc trung - cao cp c a vo th trng. T , trong nm 2016, xu hng ny cng s tip tc vi nhiu ch u t c tim lc ti chnh ln. Cc chin dch tip th, qung b ca h s dn dt th trng cn h, mc d ngun cu  phn khc thp hn vn chim lnh th trng.\r\n\r\nVi cc nh pht trin d n, yu t cnh tranh khng hn nm  chnh sch gi m cn c quyt nh bi nhiu yu t khc na, khi ngi mua ang ngy cng quan tm nhiu hn v s ci thin trong thit k, cht lng, tin ch m d n mang li v c dch v qun l sau khi d n i vo hot ng, ng MacGregor ni.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'TPHCM: Bt ng sn khu vc no s si ng trong nm 2016?', 'Trong nm 2016, BS ti qun 9 s pht trin mnh mt phn l do s ci thin ca c s h tng, k n do l cc ch u t bt u dch chuyn ra khi qun 2.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tphcm-bat-dong-san-khu-vuc-nao-se-soi-dong-trong-nam-2016', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:32:08', '2016-01-07 03:32:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=310', 0, 'post', '', 0),
