(316, 1, '2016-01-07 03:47:32', '2016-01-07 03:47:32', 'K+ l dch v truyn hnh v tinh c cung cp bi cng ty TNHH truyn hnh s v tinh Vit Nam (VSTV), lin doanh u tin gia hai c quan truyn thng hng u ca Vit Nam v Tp on Truyn thng Php l VTV/VCTV v Canal+/Canal Overseas.\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/truyen-hinh-k-2.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-tX9t"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1137" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/truyen-hinh-k-2.jpg" alt="truyen-hinh-k-2" width="623" height="432" /></a>\r\n\r\nng dng nn tng DTH (direct-to-home) v nhng cng ngh truyn hnh tin tin nht trn th gii hin nay, dch v truyn hnh v tinh K+ ph sng ton quc, mang li s khc bit v cht lng hnh nh v m thanh cng ngh s.\r\n\r\nK+ hin cung cp hn 70 knh truyn hnh SD v 10 knh truyn hnh  nt cao HD c bn quyn thuc y  cc th loi ni dung nh tin tc, gii tr tng hp, th thao, m nhc, phim truyn, khoa hc, thiu nhi\r\n\r\nK+ p ng nhu cu gii tr khc nhau ca khn gi truyn hnh vi hai la chn linh hot v gi cc l Access+ v Premium HD+\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Internet-truyen-hinh-cap-viet-nam.png" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-tX9t"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1133" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Internet-truyen-hinh-cap-viet-nam.png" alt="Internet-truyen-hinh-cap-viet-nam" width="702" height="399" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Gioi-Thieu-Cong-Ty-ThuongHieu-Kplus_725x7701.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-tX9t"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1132" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Gioi-Thieu-Cong-Ty-ThuongHieu-Kplus_725x7701.jpg" alt="Gioi-Thieu-Cong-Ty-ThuongHieu-Kplus_725x770" width="725" height="770" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>K+ ph sng rng khp:</strong>\r\n\r\nVi vic ng dng cng ngh DTH, K+ ph sng dch v trn ton lnh th Vit Nam.\r\n\r\nKhn gi c th xem cc knh truyn hnh do K+ cung cp khp mi min t nc t cc vng ni cao, hi o xa xi hay n cc thnh ph ln.\r\n\r\nK+ cng  thit lp v pht trin mng li bn hng hin i v truyn thng vi hn 2.800 im bn l v i l phn phi, cc ca hng K+ store ti H Ni, thnh ph H Ch Minh,  Nng, Cn Th, Hi Phng, Qung Ninh.\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/truyen-hinh-fpt-k-.png" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-tX9t"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1136" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/truyen-hinh-fpt-k-.png" alt="truyen hinh fpt k+" width="1901" height="801" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Banner_Dau_thu_HD_Kplus950x2941.png" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-tX9t"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1131" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Banner_Dau_thu_HD_Kplus950x2941.png" alt="Banner_Dau_thu_HD_Kplus(950x294)" width="951" height="295" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>K+ ph hp vi mi nhu cu:</strong>\r\n\r\nK+ cung cp 2 gi dch v cho khch hng la chn: Access+, Premium HD+ ph hp vi mc thu nhp v nhu cu xem truyn hnh khc nhau ca khn gi vi mc ph ch t 85.000ng/thng.\r\n\r\nB thit b gii m SD v HD ca K+ c cht lng cao v mc gi cnh tranh.\r\n\r\nD dng gia hn thu bao thng qua vic s dng th co v cc hnh thc thanh ton linh hot: thanh ton trc tip, thanh ton qua th ATM v thu ph thu bao ti nh, thanh ton theo thng.\r\n\r\nVit ha ni dung cc knh truyn hnh nc ngoi pht sng trn K+ vi cc hnh thc ph , thuyt minh hoc lng ting gip khn gi thng thc trn vn ni dung chng trnh.\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/150107-Web380x5351-011.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-tX9t"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1130" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/150107-Web380x5351-011.jpg" alt="150107-Web(380x535)1-01" width="792" height="1115" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>K+ khc bit v cht lng v dch v:</strong>\r\n\r\nBng vic u t chin lc vo cng ngh DTH v h tng c s k thut hin i, K+ m bo cung cp cho khch hng hnh nh v m thanh cht lng cao, cho c cc gi knh SD v HD.\r\n\r\nTin phong i mi vi vic cung cp dch v truyn hnh cao cp chun SD v HD vi cng mt mc ph thu bao.\r\n\r\nLa chn cc knh trong nc v quc t hay nht nhm m bo cht lng ni dung v v bn knh truyn hnh cao cp sn xut ring cho K+: K+1 , K+PM, K+NS v K+PC.\r\n\r\nDch v Chm sc Khch hng hiu qu vi i ng nhn vin chm sc khch hng tn tnh v chuyn nghip.\r\n\r\n<em>Lin h:</em><em>Tng 15/Thp A/Ta nh Resco/521 Kim M/H Ni, </em><em>in thoi: 1900  1592.</em>', 'Truyn hnh s v tinh K+', 'K+ l dch v truyn hnh v tinh c cung cp bi cng ty TNHH truyn hnh s v tinh Vit Nam (VSTV), lin doanh u tin gia hai c quan truyn thng hng u ca Vit Nam v Tp on Truyn thng Php l  VTV/VCTV v Canal+/Canal Overseas.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'truyen-hinh-so-ve-tinh-k', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:47:32', '2016-01-07 03:47:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=316', 0, 'post', '', 0),
