(326, 1, '2016-01-07 03:56:48', '2016-01-07 03:56:48', '<h5>Cho con mt nn tng, vng vng c tng lai</h5>\r\n<span dir="ltr"> Lm th no  con ng hc vn ca con khng b tr ngi bt chp nhng ri ro trong cuc sng?</span>\r\n\r\n Lm th no  chun b hiu qu cho tng lai hc vn ca con khi chi ph gio dc khng ngng gia tng?\r\n\r\nL cha m, khng c nim hnh phc no to ln hn khi nhn thy con mnh khn ln v thnh t. V th, u t cho tng lai hc vn ca con lun l mi quan tm hng u ngay t khi con mi cho i. Lm th no  thc hin c tm nguyn ny lun l trn tr ca nhiu bc cha m.\r\n\r\nThu hiu nhng bn khon ny, Prudential Vit Nam gii thiu Ph-ng Khoa Thnh Ti, mt gii php tit kim v bo v u vit, gip m bo ngun ti chnh vng chc cho tnglai hc vn ca con, ng thi mang n cho gia nh s an tm trc nhng ri ro trong cuc sng.\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/agribank-01.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-DPq0"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6506" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/agribank-01.jpg" alt="agribank-01" width="496" height="745" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. QUYN LI HC VN</strong>\r\n\r\nVi k hoch tit kim u n cng Ph-ng Khoa Thnh Ti, bn s sm m bo cho con mt qu hc vn gi tr trong tng lai.\r\n\r\nBn c th la chn thi im nhn Quyn li hc vn  ph hp vi k hoch hc tp ca con.\r\n\r\n<strong>2. QUYN LI NG KHOA</strong>\r\n\r\nKhon tin mt tr gi 10% STBH s l phn thng c bit nu con bn  i hc v nm trong danh sch cc th sinh c 10 mc im u vo cao nht ca Ngnh hc  tham gia xt tuyn (2).\r\n\r\n<strong>3. QUYN LI BO V TON DIN</strong>\r\n\r\nNu Ngi c bo him (NBH) khng may T vong hoc b Thng tt ton b v vnh vin (TTTBVV), Ph-ng Khoa Thnh Ti s mang n cho gia nh cc quyn li sau:\r\n\r\n<strong>4. QUYN LI GIA TNG BO V</strong>\r\n\r\nNhng ri ro, bt trc trong cuc sng l khng th lng trc v c th xy n vi bt k ai. Vi Ph-ng Khoa Thnh Ti, bn c th tham gia thm cc sn phm bo him b tr a dng vi mc ph thp nhm mang n cho c gia nh s bo v ton din nht trc nhng ri ro trong cuc sng nh tai nn, bnh him ngho, trang tri chi ph y t,\r\n<div>\r\n<div><em>Ch thch:</em></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n(1)BTTL l khon li cng b hng nm da trn kt qu kinh doanh ca cng ty. LCCH l khon li (nu c) c chi tr thm khi kt thc hp ng bo him.\r\n\r\n(2)<span dir="ltr">Quyn li ng khoa ch chi tr 1 ln v p dng i vi kt qu xt tuyn ca Ngi th hng Quyn li ng khoa. Ngnh hc ng k d tuyn phi thuc bc i hc (H chnh quy).</span>\r\n<div>(3)<span dir="ltr">Quyn li bo him c tr mt ln v bng 150% STBH trong trng hp NBH chnh T vong hoc b TTTBVV trc 46 tui. T ngy NBH chnh t tui 46 tr i, Quyn li bo him s bng 100% STBH.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class="the_champ_sharing_container the_champ_horizontal_sharing"></div>', 'Ph  ng Khoa Thnh Ti', 'L cha m, khng c nim hnh phc no to ln hn khi nhn thy con mnh khn ln v thnh t. V th, u t cho tng lai hc vn ca con lun l mi quan tm hng u ngay t khi con mi cho i. Lm th no  thc hin c tm nguyn ny lun l trn tr ca nhiu bc cha m.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phu-dang-khoa-thanh-tai', '', '', '2016-01-07 03:56:48', '2016-01-07 03:56:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=326', 0, 'post', '', 0),
