(332, 1, '2016-01-07 04:01:38', '2016-01-07 04:01:38', 'Khch n y ln u s khng khi bt ng v ngc nhin bi c ch qun xinh p khng ai khc chnh l n din vin L Khnh. M cc mn c t nh, n din vinC du i chinlng sc khp c hang cng ng hm  tm ra nhng qun c ngon  Si Gn. p  m mt qun c do mnh lm ch t lu, qun vi tn gi kh n s: c Khnh\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/t717535.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-xTje"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6879" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/t717535.jpg" alt="t717535" width="500" height="750" /></a>\r\n\r\nL Khnh. Din vin caC Du i Chinlun t bng b cc mn n, thc ung, phc v tn tnh cho khch. L Khnh rt quan tm n khch hng ca mnh, cng nh lun ming hi  kin ca khch hng v cc mn n. Ch chia s: Khnh mi bt u kinh doanh nn cn nhiu thiu st, nhng  kin ca khch hng rt b ch cho cng vic kinh doanh. Khnh cm n nhng  kin ng gp  v c gng hon thin  qun c phc v cho nhng thc khch ca mnh ngy mt tt hn.\r\n\r\nNgoi mn n ngon, sch s, mc gi bnh dn, c ch qun xinh p cn ngh ra cu slogan rt d thng ca qun Khng mong 1000 khch n 1 ln  Ch mong 1 khch n 1000 ln, y l cu slogan kh d thng v ng nghnh ca qun c Khnh. L gii cho cu slogan ny, n din vin xinh p tm s: Khi kinh doanh th s hi lng ca khch hng c t ln hng u, nu sau khi gh n mt ln v nhng thc khch ca mnh gh li ln th hai th  chnh l s thnh cng ca qun. Cu slogan nh mt li nhc nh Khnh v nhn vin ca qun phi lun c gng  c th phc v cho khch hng ca mnh mt cch tt nht.\r\n\r\nKhi c hi v l do m qun c, L Khnh ci v ni: Khnh rt hay i n qu vt cng bn b, c bit l khoi khu mn c. Nn khi c s ng h ca nhng ngi thn trong gia nh, Khnh  m qun c n gin ch  tha mn tnh yu c ca mnh.\r\n\r\nn y thng thc c bn s thy mt L Khnh i thng rt gin d v gn gi, ngi p tr chuyn rm r v vi thc khch, vn cng l nhng khn gi ca ch.\r\n\r\nNh bao qun c khc  Si Gn, c Khnh rt phong ph cc loi c v a dng v cch ch bin cng nh gia v. Cc mn  c Khnh bao gm: Cng gh rang mui t, c len xo da, nghu hp s, hu sng vi chanh, s lng nng m hnh, cng gh rang mui, 