(336, 1, '2016-01-07 04:03:18', '2016-01-07 04:03:18', '<h5>Mi tun Starbucks trn khp th gii phc v hng triu thc ung n tay khch hng. V Starbucks cam kt rng s phc v tng khch hng duy nht ti mt thi im.Tt c c thc ung ca Starbucks s c phc v tn tay khch hng ngay ti quy bar ca qun.y l mi lin kt gia Starbucks v khch hng.</h5>\r\nStarbucks cam kt mi lin h ny xut pht t s trn trng ca chng ti  chng ti cam kt phc v sn phm c ph vicht lng tt nht, to mi lin kt n tng khch hng v thc hin trch nhim vi cng ng v x hi ti ni Starbucks hot ng kinh doanh.Khi nghip vi mt qun chuyn bn c ph t40 nm v trc, n thi im hin ti, ti mi mt quc gia m Starbucks hng ti, mi mt a im m Starbucks d nh hot ng kinh doanh, Starbucks c gng hon thin v to dng mt mi trng tt hn nhng g m chng ti  lm.\r\n\r\n<strong>Di sn</strong>\r\n\r\nMi ngy, chng ti i lm vi hi vng thc hin hai vic: chia s ly c ph tuyt vi vi bn b v gip cho th gii hon thin hn mt cht. iu   thnh s thc khi ca hng Starbucks u tin khai trng vo nm 1971 v ngy nay, iu  cng vn gi ng nh th.Vo thi , cng ty l mt ca hng n l ti Ch Pike Place lu i  Seattle. Ch t mt mt tin ca hng hp, Starbucks  cung cp mt s loi c ph nguyn ht rang ti ngon nht th gii. Ci tn Starbucks m Moby Dick a ra  gi ln s lng mn ca bin khi v truyn thng i bin ca nhng ngi bun bn c ph thu ban u.T ly c ph Sumatra u tin ca mnh, Howard  b thu ht vo Starbucks v mt nm sau ng gia nhp cng ty.Mt nm sau, nm 1983, Howard  i ti  v b quyn r bi qun c ph  cng nh s lng mn ca tri nghim thng thc c ph.ng  c tm nhn l em qun c ph  v Hoa K. Mt ni  trao i v cm nhn v cng ng. Mt ni th ba gia cng ty v nh. ng  ri khi Starbucks trong mt thi gian ngn  bt u qun c ph Il Giornale ring ca mnh v tr li vo thng 8 nm 1987  mua Starbucks vi s tr gip ca cc nh u t a phng.\r\n\r\nT khi khi nghip, Starbucks  th hin l mt loi cng ty khc bit. Mt cng ty khng nhng ch ca ngi c ph v truyn thng phong ph m cn em li cm gic kt ni.S mnh ca chng til khi ngun cm hng v nui dng tinh thn con ngi  mt ngi, mt cc c ph v mt tnh hng xm vo mt thi im.Ngy nay, vi hn 17.400 ca hng 60 quc gia, Starbucks l nh rang xay v bn l c ph c bit hng u trn th gii. V vi mi cc c ph, chng ti c gng a c di sn ca chng ti v tri nghim c bit vo cuc sng.\r\n\r\n<strong>S mnh ca Starbucks</strong>\r\n\r\nS mnh ca chng til khi ngun cm hng v nui dng tinh thn con ngi  mt ngi, mt cc c ph v mt tnh hng xm vo mt thi im.\r\n\r\n<a title="" href="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Starbucks1.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-gallery-XG3d"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2009" src="http://unimedia.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Starbucks1.jpg" alt="Starbucks1" width="767" height="511" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Gi m ca:</strong>06:30 AM  22:00 PM\r\n\r\n<strong>in thoi:</strong>+848 3822 4206\r\n\r\n<strong>Fax:</strong>+848 3822 1030\r\n\r\n<a title="Starbucks Coffee Company" href="https://www.facebook.com/starbucksvietnam" target="_blank">Facebook</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Website:</strong><a title="Starbucks Coffee Company" href="http://www.starbucks.vn/">http://www.starbucks.vn</a>', 'Starbucks Coffee', 'Mi tun Starbucks trn khp th gii phc v hng triu thc ung n tay khch hng. V Starbucks cam kt rng s phc v tng khch hng duy nht ti mt thi im. Tt c c thc ung ca Starbucks s c phc v tn tay khch hng ngay ti quy bar ca qun. y l mi lin kt gia Starbucks v khch hng.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'starbucks-coffee', '', '', '2016-01-07 04:05:17', '2016-01-07 04:05:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tmdt/?p=336', 0, 'post', '', 0),
