(364, 1, '2016-01-18 03:46:47', '2016-01-18 03:46:47', 'D c ni dung kh nhm nhng <em>Thi t phi thng chc k</em> vn tr thnh phim hot nht trn sng truyn hnh Trung Quc trong nhng ngy qua. B phim c nhiu m n, soi ca tr p gy st cng lot cnh nng nh vo th hiu ca ngi xem.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , nhng trang phc c khi l lng, h hang, lc nhi hng hiu ba bi ca b phim ang tr thnh  ti bn tn si ni ca cng ng mng.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-0" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-0" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-1-0-1451891628598.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 1" /></span></p>\r\nCung tn m n trong phim Thi t phi thng chc k c gu <a class="TextlinkBaiviet" title="thi trang" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/thoi-trang-c78.html">thi trang</a> "mt m" v gy tranh ci\r\n\r\n<strong>Trang phc h hang n l lng</strong>\r\n\r\nD l mt b phim c trang nhng trang phc ca cc cung tn, m n trong b phim ny li v cng mt m vi nhng phn x t, khoe vai trn gi cm. Gii thch v iu ny, o din L Ho Ct Ct tng cho bit, do thi im quay phim (thng 8 va qua) qu nng nn trang phc ca din vin phi ti gin v thoi mi nht.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , cng theo ng, vic trang phc s si v c phn rt u b cho l do kinh ph khng nhiu, thi gian eo hp. Theo mt ngun tin Trung Quc, hu ht trang phc u c may t vi mua  ch hay mua trn trang bn hng Taobao.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-1" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-1" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-phuc-trang-di-va-dat-trong-loat-phim-sap-mang-xu-hoa.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 2" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Vy o ca cung phi, m n rt h hang d l phim c trang</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-2" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-2" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-13-1451891629079.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 3" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Do kinh ph eo hp, cc din vin phi t chnh sa phc trang v make up cho nhau</p>\r\n<strong>Trang phc ''nhi'' hng hiu l liu</strong>\r\n\r\nXem <em>Thi t phi thng chc k</em>, nhiu ngi khng khi ng ngng khi thy, b cnh ca nhiu nhn vt c trang nh thi t T Thnh hay ngi p Trng Bng Bng b nhi  hiu quc t mt cch l liu. C th, nhiu b  ca T Thnh b c dn mng em ra so snh vi thng hiu Hn Quc KTZ v thng hiu Craig Green hay vy ca Trng Bng Bng ging vi  ca Jean Paul Gaultier.\r\n\r\nThm ch, c nhng cnh quay, nhn vt c trang i hn m c thu logo hai ch C lng vo nhau ca thng hiu Chanel!\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-3" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-3" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-iiv5-fxnerek0958115.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 4" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">M thu logo Chanel</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-4" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-4" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-1f68-fxneefv9055294.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 5" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Trang phc ca thi t T Th ging vi mt b cnh ca thng hiu KTZ</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-5" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-5" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-fzqx-fxneefv9056235.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#39;nhi, nhm&amp;#39; trong phim &amp;#39;nng&amp;#39; nht x Hoa - 6" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Trang phc ca mt cung phi ly cm hng t vy MAMA ca Dolce &amp; Gabbana</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-6" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-6" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/1-2016/images/2016-01-06/1452071203-1452066515-phuc-trang-di-va-dat-trong-loat-phim-sap-mang-xu-hoa--1-.jpg" alt="Thi trang &amp;#3